temperatures of seven degrees centigrade, as you can see there, 45 Fahrenheit. So rather

04:34.000 --> 04:39.520
cloudy, some rain for a time. Jeremy, let's have a look at your South East at Six logo.

04:39.520 --> 04:44.080
That's rather splendid, isn't it? How long did it actually take you to get that together?

04:44.080 --> 04:45.800
About two hours.

04:46.720 --> 04:51.400
I mean, that's rather, I mean, it's very pretty, but do you think it was worth the effort?

04:51.400 --> 04:55.840
Well, yes and no. But there's actually quite a lot of complicated maths involved in that,

04:55.840 --> 04:57.560
which just doesn't show up when you look at it.

